  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="shortdesc:1;23:14">Install markdown-validator with pip in a Python virtual environment.
  After installation, the <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeph:1;24:35">md-validate</codeph> command is available from
  your terminal.</shortdesc>

  <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="taskbody:1;27:13">

    <prereq id="prereq" class="- topic/section task/prereq " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="prereq:1;29:25">
      <title class="- topic/title " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="title:2;30:14">Before you begin</title>
      <ul class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="ul:1;31:11">
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="li:1;32:13">Python 3.12 or later must be installed. To check your Python version,
        open a terminal and enter:
        <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeblock:1;34:41">python --version</codeblock>
        If Python is not installed or is older than 3.12, download it from
        <xref href="https://python.org" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="xref:1;36:72">python.org</xref>.</li>
        <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="li:2;37:13">You need access to a terminal (Command Prompt or PowerShell on Windows,
        Terminal on macOS or Linux).</li>
      </ul>
    </prereq>

    <steps class="- topic/ol task/steps " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="steps:1;42:12">

      <step id="step-venv" class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="step:1;44:28">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="cmd:1;45:14">Create and activate a virtual environment.</cmd>
        <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="info:1;46:15">
          <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="p:1;47:14">On macOS or Linux:</p>
          <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeblock:2;48:43">python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate</codeblock>
          <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="p:2;50:14">On Windows (PowerShell):</p>
          <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeblock:3;51:43">python -m venv .venv
.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1</codeblock>
          <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="p:3;53:14">When the virtual environment is active, your terminal prompt includes
          <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeph:2;54:19">(.venv)</codeph>.</p>
        </info>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="stepresult:1;56:21">The virtual environment is active. Packages you install now
        go into this isolated environment.</stepresult>
      </step>

      <step id="step-pip" class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="step:2;60:27">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="cmd:2;61:14">Install markdown-validator.</cmd>
        <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="info:2;62:15">
          <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeblock:4;63:43">pip install markdown-validator</codeblock>
        </info>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="stepresult:2;65:21">pip downloads and installs markdown-validator and its
        dependencies.</stepresult>
      </step>

      <step id="step-verify" class="- topic/li task/step " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="step:3;69:30">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="cmd:3;70:14">Verify the installation.</cmd>
        <info class="- topic/itemgroup task/info " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="info:3;71:15">
          <codeblock xml:space="preserve" class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeblock:5;72:43">md-validate --version</codeblock>
        </info>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="stepresult:3;74:21">The terminal displays the installed version number, confirming
        that the tool is ready to use.</stepresult>
      </step>

    </steps>

    <result id="result" class="- topic/section task/result " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="result:1;80:25">
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="p:4;81:10">markdown-validator is installed. You can now run
      <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeph:3;82:15">md-validate validate</codeph> from this terminal session whenever
      the virtual environment is active.</p>
    </result>

    <postreq id="postreq" class="- topic/section task/postreq " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="postreq:1;86:27">
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="p:5;87:10">If your team's rule set uses sentence-count (<codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeph:4;87:63">s</codeph>) or
      part-of-speech (<codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="codeph:5;88:31">p&lt;N&gt;</codeph>) rules, also run:
      <xref href="t_download-nltk.dita" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="xref:2;89:41">Download NLTK language data</xref>.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p " xtrf="file:/Volumes/Matt_files/Git/mb/markdown-validator/docs-user/user-guide/tasks/t_install.dita" xtrc="p:6;90:10">Ready to validate:
